function Experience() { return (<>

Experience Details

  • Assistant Professor, Department of Mathematical Sciences, Karakoram International University Gilgit, Pakistan (July, 2013 - June 2019)

  • Volunteer Lecturer, University of Science and Technology Beijing, China (Semester fall, 2012)

  • Lecturer, Department of Mathematical Sciences,Karakoram International University Gilgit, Pakistan (March 2006 - July 2013)

  • Reviewing articles for several international SCI and EI journals)

  • HEC Approved Ph.D Supervisor .(2015 - present)

  • Departmental Graduate Advisor, Department of Mathematical Sciences, Karakoram International University Gilgit, Pakistan)

  • Coordinator and Founding Editor-in-Chief, KIU research journal "Journal of Mountain Area Research")

  • Consultant, United Nations (United Nations Observer/Monitor for 6th census of Pakistan). (March 2017 - April 2017)

  • Head of department, Department of Mathematical Sciences, Karakoram International University Gilgit (2016 - 2017)

  • Chairman, Department of Mathematical Sciences, Karakoram International University Gilgit (2018 - present)

  • Associate Professor, Department of Mathematical Sciences, Karakoram International University Gilgit (June, 2019 - present)

); } export default Experience;
